DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-07T21:15:00&endDate=2026-06-08T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMILDMAY LINE: Sunday 7 June\, from 2215\, no service between Camden Road and Stratford. Replacement bus service S operates between Camden Road and Stratford via Holloway Road (for Piccadilly line)\, Highbury & Islington (for Caledonian Road & Barnsbury)\, Canonbury (St Pauls Road)\, Dalston Junction (for Dalston Kingsland)\, Hackney Central\, Homerton and Hackney Wick. Some of the westbound buses will continue\, if required by passengers at Camden Road\, all stations to Richmond\, except Brondesbury Park (bus calls at Queens Park instead)
